$(c,b,t)$ all signs + running & 216 & $0.0079$ & $0.09$ \\
$(s,c,b)$ signed, self~\citep{Rivero2011} & 4 & $0.0305$ & $14$ \\
Adj.\ chain, sign rule, no run & 3 & $0.0402$ & $9.2$ \\
Adj.\ chain, sign rule + run & 594 & $0.083$ & $0.5$ \\
Adj.\ chain, all signs + run & 2{,}376 & $0.120$ & $0.5$ \\
20 triples, self $(+,+,+)$ & 20 & $0.206$ & $8.6$ \\
