\midrule
Lepton Koide                          & $\sim 10^{-5}$       & $6 \times 10^{-6}$   & $\sim 6 \times 10^{-6}$ & $\approx 1$  & converging since 1981 \\
Rivero $(s, c, b)$ signed self        & $8.2 \times 10^{-3}$ & $7.5 \times 10^{-3}$ & $5.4 \times 10^{-4}$    & $\approx 14$ & stable; non-convergent \\
