$(s,c,b)$ & $s@2m_\tau$, $c@m_\tau$, $b@m_H$ & $(-,+,+)$ & $0.66674$ & $6.9 \times 10^{-5}$ & $0.13$ \\
$(u,s,c)$ & $u@(m_\tau{+}m_c)$, $s@m_c$, $c@m_b$ & $(-,+,+)$ & $0.66658$ & $9.0 \times 10^{-5}$ & $0.17$ \\
